STEP3:
tools->build system->new build system  define the file: untitled.sublime-build

-----BEGIN CONTENT-----
{ 
"cmd": ["/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.6/bin/python3", "-u", "$file"], 
"file_regex": "^[ ]*File \"(...*?)\", line ([0-9])*", 
"selector": "source.python" 
}
-----END CONTENT--------
----NOTE:MAC system,how get the path of python3,Termial input:which python3------

SAVE the file as python3.sublime-build

tools->build system->python3
view->syntax->python

STEP4:
package install:
Prefences->package control->install package:
SublimeREPL
Bracket Highlighter
SublimeLinter
CodeIntel

pip3 install --upgrade --pre CodeIntel
